    stem: "A 70-year-old male with acute decompensated HFrEF (EF 15%, cardiogenic shock, MAP 55 mmHg, CI 1.6 L/min/m², on dobutamine with inadequate response) is started on milrinone. What is milrinone's mechanism, and why is it classified as an 'inodilator' rather than a pure inotrope?",
